body:
Hello, {{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 


My name is Nahsti,
a low elo player that is still quite new to LoL (Year and a half) and currently permanently banned on my main account and a second account of my four accounts I have, obviously by the title you know what this is about but let me explain why and my intention of doing so.

{{champion:35}} 

Last year during a game where I had people being toxic to me in a normal game I got myself banned from me sending vulgar responses to this premade
and being multi-reported ended my main account and since than my 2nd account got banned (this happened while I was away for Christmas so I don&#039;t know what caused it to be banned nor even it was because of me, still need to look into it)

{{champion:72}} 

The reason I&#039;m writing this is to send a serious apology out to the people I&#039;ve played with and against, personal friends and random people alike that had to witness or became victim to these acts and words such as swearing, discrimination and int feeding/AFK.

{{champion:117}} 

When I started League I swore I would never become an Inter/AFK&#039;er nor would I ever rage especially out loud, but obviously this happened multiple times over and over, not only have I lost 2 account to these acts but I&#039;ve also lost 2 computer screens, a laptop, 3 keyboards, 4 gaming mice, chair and what I think should be around nearly or over $2000 on champions and skins not even kidding this may be wrong but it&#039;s defiantly around this.

{{champion:41}} 

I have real anger, mental health and learning issues that effect my life every day and create obstacles that the average persons doesn&#039;t have to deal with and I know that some may see this as too personal too post but the reason I&#039;m doing so is that I&#039;m putting serious effort into my life to turn this around and I&#039;m not ashamed of that, and this includes my gaming activities and communities as well and the chance that people that have come across me will see this post may be minimal but still it&#039;s out there *HELLO*

{{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}} 

What do I expect out of this?:
Nothing really, a few troll posts, some a$$ hat posts really because it is the internet after all, so I won&#039;t bother reading comments. Do I expect this to get me unbanned? haha of course not and this isn&#039;t an attempt to be thought it would be nice, I don&#039;t have some fan base like Tyler1 or something but it is something that needs to be done in my opinion and I feel a lot better about doing it.

I&#039;m currently playing as a reformed player and person and getting a lot better games and elo climbing is a lot smoother right now and I hope it is the same for everyone else.

I wish I could give some advice for people that may experience the same stuff but really the only answer is to shut up, mute toxic people and gank often,
Just stick to the triple P&#039;s.

{{summoner:6}} 

POSITIVE
PRODUCTIVE
PERSISTENT


{{summoner:4}} 

Don&#039;t ever give up and never stop trying, especially on a late game champion! {{champion:67}} 

Anyone that reads this, thank you for your time, and preemptively for anyone writing a positive comment or sending out any positive support in anyway thank you :)

I know things in this post may be all over the place and not totally make sense but again I have learning issues I&#039;ve had all my life and this is the best I can do. :)

P.S. For those wondering about how I&#039;ve spent so much on this account, I do work and I work hard. I don&#039;t loath on any government benefits and feed everything in to gaming.


Nahsti.     {{champion:201}}
